{
  "title": "Designate specific users to access the report for a shared mailbox",
  "slug": "designate-specific-users-to-clean-up-the-report-for-a-shared-mailbox",
  "categorySlug": "organisational-roll-out",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Designate specific users to access the report for a shared mailbox</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\"></h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>With Admin Light permissions, there is an option to designate which users should be responsible for cleaning up cleanup reports for shared mailboxes.</p>\n<p>Open the menu \"Production\". At the bottom, there is a list of accounts being scanned. Here, open the \"shared\" tab to see a list of all shared mailboxes. By clicking on the three dots next to the account's name, a window will appear where you can add the user you want to be able to view the cleanup report for that specific shared mailbox:</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"201\" style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=816&amp;height=201&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png\" width=\"816\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=408&amp;height=101&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png 408w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=816&amp;height=201&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png 816w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=1224&amp;height=302&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png 1224w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=1632&amp;height=402&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png 1632w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=2040&amp;height=503&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png 2040w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png?width=2448&amp;height=603&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-48-5359-PM.png 2448w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 816px) 100vw, 816px\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"282\" style=\"width: 557px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://lh7-us.googleusercontent.com/f0XbdZYEIW7qqx4hIbRK3Rbmx7yEKbPpC7BeDyaC6Oypv6pGccPmcNyVO9I8dOfpxU3I0U_5PBd86xgSplmF4njyDBy4sqFqL0x_MM4GcvQVvjR0q9iR6Pt5FbOpqehcyz2bwwq8w2aEG82IHv5RbeQ\" width=\"557\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>Subsequently, the designated user will be able to see both their own data in the cleanup report and data for the shared mailbox:</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"135\" style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=350&amp;height=135&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png\" width=\"350\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=175&amp;height=68&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png 175w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=350&amp;height=135&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png 350w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=525&amp;height=203&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png 525w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=700&amp;height=270&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png 700w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=875&amp;height=338&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png 875w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png?width=1050&amp;height=405&amp;name=image-png-Nov-07-2024-12-05-42-5678-PM.png 1050w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\"></p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
